<section class="section">
  <h2>Add a New Patch</h2>
  <p>PatchBook is content-driven. Add a markdown file in <code>src/patches/</code> and redeploy.</p>
  <h3>Required frontmatter</h3>
  <pre><code>---
slug: your-slug
title: "Your patch title"
tags: ["netlify", "build"]
applies_to: ["node", "netlify"]
risk: "low"
permalink: false
---
</code></pre>
  <h3>Where to put it</h3>
  <p>Create <code>src/patches/your-slug.md</code> and include your patch content below frontmatter.</p>
</section>
